  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个刷新Token的完整流程图，从客户端发起刷新请求开始，到最终返回新Token为止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client Refresh Request"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这个流程应该包括验证、缓存检查、过期判断这些环节对吧？我先画个起点框。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client Refresh Request"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，起点就叫\"客户端刷新请求\"。第一步是验证Refresh Token的有效性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Validate Refresh Token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我在起点后面加了一个处理节点，标注验证Refresh Token。接下来需要一个判断分支吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Validate Refresh Token",
        "Refresh Token Valid?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，这里要有个菱形判断框\"Refresh Token是否有效\"。如果无效，直接返回401未授权。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Refresh Token Valid?",
        "Return 401 Unauthorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，无效分支指向返回401的终止节点。我把它标成红色背景。有效的话继续走什么流程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Return 401 Unauthorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有效的话要去缓存里查这个Token，加一个\"检查Token是否在缓存中\"的节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check Token in Cache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "检查缓存节点加好了。这里也需要分支判断对吧？找不到Token的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check Token in Cache",
        "Token Found in Cache?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，菱形判断\"Token是否在缓存中找到\"。找不到的话返回401 Token未找到。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Token Found in Cache?",
        "Return 401 Token Not Found"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，这个错误分支我也标红了。找到了的话下一步是判断过期时间？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Return 401 Token Not Found",
        "Token Not Expired?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，第三个菱形判断\"Token是否未过期\"。如果过期了返回401 Token已过期。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Token Not Expired?",
        "Return 401 Token Expired"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "过期分支画好了，也是红色。三个错误分支都齐了。那Token有效且未过期的话，进入生成新Token的阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Return 401 Token Expired",
        "Generate New Access Token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，先生成新的Access Token，然后紧接着生成新的Refresh Token。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Generate New Access Token",
        "Generate New Refresh Token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "两个生成节点连好了。接下来要把新的Refresh Token存到缓存里吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Store New Refresh Token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，加\"存储新Refresh Token\"节点。然后别忘了把旧的Refresh Token标记为失效。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Store New Refresh Token",
        "Invalidate Old Refresh Token"
