      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "存储和失效两个节点都加上了。最后还要更新用户会话缓存？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Update User Session Cache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，加\"更新用户会话缓存\"，然后最终返回200 OK带上新的两个Token。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Update User Session Cache",
        "Return 200 OK with New Tokens"
