      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说的\"Token Not Expired\"这个判断，语义上容易歧义。应该是\"Token未过期\"走Yes分支，但字面看\"Not Expired\"是双重否定。",
      "elements_involved": [
